WALLPAPER-ENGINE transforms your boring static desktop into a living, 
breathing workspace. Unlike the paid Steam version costing $4.99, this 
GitHub release gives you 100% FREE access to thousands of animated 
wallpapers with zero watermarks and zero limitations.

The software runs silently in your system tray with only 1-3% CPU usage,
ensuring your gaming and work performance stays smooth. It automatically 
pauses animations when running full-screen applications (games, movies) 
to save resources — then resumes when you return to desktop.

